data.title: Blind Swine Lounge
data.meta_site_name: Blind Swine - Duck Creek & Monkey Island
data.text:
Open Tuesday thru Saturday 4pm to 2am

Serving Food 'til 11pm Tues - Thurs & 1am Fri & Sat!

A couple of changes... we're 21 & over only... taking it back to the original Blind Swine concept!

"Craft Cocktail Lounge - Late Night Eatery - Live Music Venue"

We've also gone non-smoking indoors but have an outdoor area to accommodate!

A brand new FULL SERVICE RESTAURANT on the North end is coming soon! More details to follow.

Thanks for your continued support and your patience. More great things are on the way. Hope to see you soon!
